Overview of Changes from BTK+ 2.24.21 to 2.24.22
================================================

* Look in /usr/share/btk-2.0 for the default btkrc file

* Support building with automake 1.14

* Translation updates:
 Hungarian


Overview of Changes from BTK+ 2.24.20 to 2.24.21
================================================

* OS X: Various input handling fixes
 - Avoid a crash on first key press
 - Fall back from native input method to BtkIMContextSimple
 - Avoid beeping when using native input method
 - Reset preedit state when needed

* Look for btkrc in /usr/share/btk-2.0, in addition to to system config
  dirs

* Bug fixes:
 513812 Optimize bdk_bairo_set_source_pixbuf() alpha multiplication...
 536767 btksignal.h includes btk.h
 692548 Quartz: Cursor doesn't reset when the mouse leaves a toplev...
 695636 _bdk_windowing_create_bairo_surface() may return already fi...
 698758 Wrong limit for "Native Windows wider or taller than 65535 ...
 699236 Assert triggered during bdk_pixmap_new() if some failure ha...
 699673 [3.2/3.4/3.6/3.8] uuid conflicting on Windows
 701332 Patch for minor glitch in NSTextInput
 701571 1ad25dfb causes NSApp to not notice NSWindow destruction
 703789 btk.immodules still referenced after switch to immodules.cache
 705181 Annoying beep on arrow keys when using IME on MacOS
 705182 Reset Cocoa IME state when immodule is reset

* Translation updates:
 Thai


Overview of Changes from BTK+ 2.24.19 to 2.24.20
================================================

* Backport changes from BTK+ 3 to look for rc files in system
  config dirs in addition to /etc/btk-2.0 and ~/.btkrc.

* Backport changes from BTK+ 3 to look for the immodules cache
  file in libdir. btk-query-immodules-2.0 gained an --update-cache
  option to write the output to the correct location. Note that
  this may require slight adjustment of distro packaging.

* Bug fixes:
 560337 BtkFileChooser hour time missing for current date files
 649390 CRLF text is copied to clipboard as CRCRLF on Windows
 698183 quartz: Text input is too slow and some keys are broken...
 702455 Add support for Avahi printers to btk 2.24.x

* Translation updates:
 Polish


