Overview of Changes from BTK+ 2.24.10 to 2.24.11
================================================

* X11:
 - Use _NET_WM_STATE_HIDDEN for iconification when supported

* Win32:
 - Don't drash when installed in a top-level directory

* Quartz:
 - Make function keys work
 - Fix the build on OS X 10.7
 - Fix manual resizing of windows
 - Handle some key events better (such as dead tilde)

* Bugs fixed:
 603559 btk should handle missing immodules better
 640308 BtkStatusIcon never emits plug-removed on socket
 643131 btk_tray_icon_dispose
 655065 Build failure on OS X 10.7 Lion
 667155 Demos in btk2 don't comply with gseal
 670093 bdk_window_get_screen() not documented in new symbols
 670400 First shortcut capture is broken
 672125 btk_enumerate_printers() doesn't call the destroy no...
