 Indonesian
 Polish
 Spanish


Overview of Changes from BTK+ 2.24.3 to 2.24.5
==============================================

* Annotation fixes

* Update some deprecation notes and porting hints

* Bugs fixed:
 576492 BtkBuilder does not respect G_PARAM_CONSTRUCT properties
 637304 Name Contains Entry is not exposing accessibility
 647908 btkrc does not handle "shade()" in a locale safe manor
 648931 Bdk clipboard doesn't work correctly
 652102 Issues when redrawing multiple BdkWindows
 652239 resurect Windows clipboard selection notification
 652402 btkdnd unbinds all key grabs
        Ensure we always grab the lock in async callbacks
        Use an existing mimetype for the BTK_FILE stock icon
        Fix missing icons in the builtin icon theme
        Fix the build without XSHM
        Fix the build against recent GLib

* Translation updates:
 Dutch
 Norwegian bokmål


Overview of Changes from BTK+ 2.24.2 to 2.24.3
==============================================

* Add missing introspection annotations

* Fix BtkComboBoxEntry accessibility support

* Thread-safety fixes in file chooser and app chooser code

* Fix some deficiencies with the builtin icon theme

* Translation updates
 Dutch
 Norwegian bokmål


