Overview of Changes from BTK+ 2.24.0 to 2.24.1
==============================================

* BTK+ now refuses to load modules that are linked against
  the wrong BTK+ version, preventing BTK_PATH accidents.

* A number of memory leaks and segfaults involving accessibility
  have been fixed.

* Bugs fixed:
 599907 Bail implementation of batk_add_key_event_listener return...
 626730 Check menu item does not set indeterminate state
 633291 Handle Shift-keys in X11 bdk_test_simulate_key()
 640487 crash on btk_statusbar_remove_all()
 640992 Missed Return Type in btk/btkrange.c: btk_range_set_round_digits
 642137 btk+-2.24.0 requires Xcomposite.h
 642642 Missed include in btk/btkmodules.c
 642681 btk_combo_box_text_get_active_text doesn't work as stated
 642772 BTK does not correctly process input sent via SendInput...

* Translation updates:
 Hungarian
 Polish


Overview of Changes from BTK+ 2.23.90 to 2.24.0
===============================================

* BtkBuilder has gained support for
 - items in BtkComboBoxText
 - tags in BtkTextTagTable
 - menus in BtkMenuToolButton

* The btk-builder-convert script gained a
  --target-version option

* Many introspection annotation fixes

* Bugs fixed:
 351755 BTK_RANGE (range) -> round_digits should be exposed...
 590459 Text is sometimes not pasted at the right location
 639327 btk-builder-convert needs to convert btkcomboboxentry...
 634677 assertion in finalize assuring that buffer is NULL...

* Updated translations:
