* New deprecations:
 - bdk_set_pointer_hooks(), bdk_display_set_pointer_hooks()
 - btk_range_get/set_update_policy()
 - btk_window_get/set_frame_dimensions() and
   btk_window_get/set_has_frame()

* The cups print backend can now send print jobs directly in PDF if
  cups supports it

