Overview of Changes from BTK+ 2.21.5 to 2.21.6
==============================================

* Most drawing done by BTK+ itself has been ported from
  BDK drawing APIs to bairo

* BtkExpander gained a ::label-fill property to make the label
  fill the entire horizontal space

* Deprecations:
 - BtkNotebookPage
 - The BtkRecenManager::limit property
 - All BDK drawing functions, ie bdk_draw_*. Use bairo instead
 - All BdkGC functions. Use bairo instead
 - All of BdkImage. Use bairo instead
 - All of BdkRGB. Use bairo instead
 - bdk_{bit,pix}map_create_from_data

* New accessors:
 - bdk_cursor_get_cursor_type
 - bdk_device_get_n_axes
 - bdk_display_is_closed
 - btk_notebook_get_tab_[hv]border

* New bairo-related APIs:
 - bdk_window_create_similar_surface
 - bdk_window_get_background_pattern

* Accessiblity:
 - Make Bail work with custom treemodels
 - Implement BailAdjustment::get_minimum_increment

* Bugs fixed:
 599574 Crash in _bairo_surface_set_error
 604391 ...assertion `ancestor != NULL' when switching between tab
 618327 BtkNotebookPage should be deprecated
 623603 meld built with pybtk-2.16.0 giving warnings
 623865 btkdnd: pointer grab may never finish (ungrab before grab)
 624087 Missing accessor for BdkCursor.type
 624221 Btk-2.21 Missing accessor for BdkDevice.num_axis
 624224 Missing accessor for BdkDisplay.closed
 624333 Deprecate BtkRecentManager:limit
 624687 switch-page bug when activated from menu
 624779 BtkCalendar padding/margin/spacing/border/whatever is too hard...
 625491 Generate BdkX11-2.0.typelib (backported from HEAD)
 625650 Add annotations to btk_tree_model_iter_next() and btk_tree_sel...

* Translation updates:
 Norwegian bokmål


