* GSeal:
 - Deprecate widget flag macros
   BTK_WIDGET_STATE
   BTK_WIDGET_SAVED_STATE
   BTK_WIDGET_FLAGS
   BTK_WIDGET_TOPLEVEL
   BTK_WIDGET_NO_WINDOW
   BTK_WIDGET_COMPOSITE_CHILD
   BTK_WIDGET_APP_PAINTABLE
   BTK_WIDGET_CAN_DEFAULT
   BTK_WIDGET_CAN_FOCUS
   BTK_WIDGET_DOUBLE_BUFFERED
   BTK_WIDGET_HAS_DEFAULT
   BTK_WIDGET_HAS_GRAB
   BTK_WIDGET_RECEIVES_DEFAULT
 - Also deprecate the type macros
   BTK_WIDGET_TYPE
   BTK_OBJECT_TYPE_NAME
   BTK_OBJECT_TYPE

* BtkOffscreenWindow: A new toplevel container widget to manage
  offscreen rendering of child widgets

* OS X:
 - Memory leak fixes and other improvements

