 Swedish
 Thai
 Ukrainian


Overview of Changes from BTK+ 2.19.1 to 2.19.2
==============================================

* Introspection:
 - Introspection data for bdk-pixbuf, bdk and btk is now
   included in BTK+ itself. As a consequence, the batk dependency
   has been bumped to 2.29.2, and a bobject-introspection dependency
   has been added. configure with --disable-introspection in order
   to not build introspection data.

* Client-side windows:
 - Fix some issues with handling of button and motion events
 - Fix damage reporting for drawing on offscreen windows
 - Fix problems with handling of input extension events

* Printing:
 - Add api to handle printer hard margins

* Simple IM Context:
 - Sync with Xorg compose file
 - Make Compose-vowel-minus combinations consistent

* BDK:
 - bdk_screen_get_primary_monitor: New function to get the
   'primary' monitor in a multi-monitor setup

* bdk-pixbuf has gained the ability to store and retrieve embedded
  ICC color profiles in png and tiff images

* Keyboard handling:
 - Mnemonic underlines can now optionally be hidden until the Alt key
   is pressed, this can be turned on with the btk-auto-mnemonics setting
 - Using the Super, Meta and Hyper modifiers in accelerators is working
   more reliably

* Bugs fixed:
 603652 Sporadic crashes with BtkSocket
 605008 the rebunnyion of damage event doesn't be copied in bdk_event_copy
 588554 only show the accelerator when pressing alt
 601473 BDK_BUTTON?_MOTION_MASK appears to be broken
 601712 Add API for determining primary monitor
  50942 selection/arrow key improvement
 427409 editing shortcut always fails with super key
 468989 need a way to get the printer's hard margins
 502266 btk_tree_selection_get_selected_rows free example produces...
 592279 Introspection support
 597386 Cannot click buttons more than once without moving the mouse...
 599213 Use BtkCellEditable:editing_canceled property instead...
 599397 Button stuck at pressed look after screen rotation
 601383 btk_icon_view_get_selected_items: example code gives...
 602099 Actions can be activatable too
 603619 the colormap of offscreen's pixmap doesn't inherit...
 603904 bdk_draw_line doesn't have expose area.
 604117 Add info about single includes when compiling BTK+ apps
 604289 Please permit progress pages to be final in a dialog
 604462 btktoolitem.c: return-value is different type
 604747 Using bdk_draw_line, the expose area of damage event is wrong
 604787 property-notify-event is not delivered to a non-toplevel...
 604881 BtkCellEditable::editing-cancelled should be writable
 591085 BtkBuilder object ID bounded to BtkWidget "name" property

* Updated translations:
 Arabic
 Estonian
 Hebrew
 Low German
 Norwegian bokmål
 Slovenian
 Spanish
 Telugu
 Vietnamese


Overview of Changes from BTK+ 2.19.0 to 2.19.1
==============================================

* Client-side windows:
 - Avoid some unnecessary exposes
 - Avoid unnecessary redraws related to clearing windows

* BtkNotebook gained an 'action area'

* BtkStatusbar gained a 'message area'

* BtkToolPalette is a new container to show tool items
  in collapsible groups in a grid

* bdk-pixbuf can now handle compressed TIFF images

* GSEAL work:
 - New accessor: btk_window_get_window_type()

* Bugs fixed:
 590017  Does not compile under MinGW32 + Wine
 569430 Bail should include a reciprocal relationship for NODE_CHILD_OF
 598758 Need context for a propper translation
 594535 No accesor for BtkStatusbar->label and ->frame
 602725 fix setting icon-size on GICON images
 599402 Landscape and Reverse Landscape icons need to be swapped
 588740 JPEG images open with blur effect?
 601337 Only use bdk_input_select_events() if XINPUT_NONE is defined
 598050 Flickering in a btk_socket
 600158 Do not use static GTypeInfo and GInterfaceInfo
 561973 Problem dragging images from Firefox to BTK+ app on Windows
 601512 Remove unnecessary check in BtkTreeModelFilter
 600222 Check for existence of bairo-svg.h in configure.in
 595498 No accesor for BTK_WINDOW ()->type
 116650 "action area" for BtkNotebook (e.g. for tab close button)
 600150 BtkColorSelection tooltip issues
