 Swedish


Overview of Changes from BTK+ 2.18.x to 2.19.0
==============================================

* A throbber widget and cell renderer have been added: BtkSpinner and
  BtkCellRendererSpinner

* BtkFileSystemModel has been reimplemented, for major speedups and
  other improvements

* Synchronize compose sequences with the current X.org Compose file

* Win32:
 - The GDI+ image loader works again
 - XP themes have been disabled since they don't work currently

* OS X:
 - Fix crashes due to unimplemented BdkWindowImplIface methods
 - Use standard Mac keyboard shortcuts (Cmx-X, Cmd-C instead of
   Ctrl-X, Ctrl-C, etc)
 - Add a pixbuf loader for the QTIF format
 - Improve multi-monitor handling

* GSEAL work:
 - New accessor for BtkDialog buttons: btk_dialog_get_widget_for_response
 - New accessor for BtkViewport bin_window: btk_viewport_get_bin_window
 - Add a BtkCellEditable::editing-canceled property

* Deprecations:
 - BtkInputDialog has been deprecated
 - BtkCurve and BtkGammaCurve have been deprecated
 - The tab-packing feature in BtkNotebook has been deprecated

* Bugs fixed:
 594644 Cannot compile BTK+ with MinGW 4.4.0
 581150 BtkIconView tries to paint items with invalid sizes
 598881 Unimplemented BdkWindowImplIface methods crash gimp on OSX
 598218 Substitute deprecated btk_*_ref/unref calls
 381371 Print margins not correct in WIN32 - not allowing for...
 597596 Toolbar button accessible objects don't have label name
 599118 Translators comment for "Finishing" labels
 598261 Add support to BtkTooltip to handle GIcons
 530351 Use standard mac shortcuts
 597865 Move documentation from templates to inline comments
 596083 Deprecate notebook label packing functionality
 594903 Deprecate BtkInputDialog
 599403 Avoid using accel group internals in BtkSocket
 590800 The window content is not updated correctly when scrolling
 598515 Do not assign the BtkSpinner parent class twice
 552678 gdi+ pixbuf loaders fail on "large" images
 598217 Substitute deprecated bdk_*_ref/unref calls
 596238 Make Quartz backend properly implement the BdkScreen...
 599446 batk_object_set_name () assertion in btk_tool_button_set_label
 592582 Print preview doesn't reflect the printout
 563010 BtkFileChooserButton cannot have none file selected again
 596019 No accesors for BtkDialog buttons
 366217 Add QTIF image support
 594962 No accessor for BTK_ENTRY (entry)->editing_canceled

* Updated translations:
