Overview of Changes from BTK+ 2.16.0 to 2.16.1
==============================================

* BtkBuilder:
 - Accessible action names can now be marked as translatable.
 - btk-builder-convert correctly handles response ids in all dialogs.
 - btk-builder-convert warns about duplicate ids.

* BDK:
 - BDK no longer refuses to work on 30-bit visuals

* Win32:
 - The appearance of BTK+ menus on Vista has been improved.

