Overview of Changes from BTK+ 2.13.5 to 2.13.6
==============================================

* Fix problems on 64-bit Windows

* Fix a long-standing, well-known problem with the handling
  of insensitive buttons, bug 56070

* Fallback to Xinerama if the Xrandr implementation
  is just a stub

* bdk_threads_add_timeout_seconds[_full]: New functions with
  second-granularity to complete the set of bdk_threads_ timeout
  functions

* Support rendering icons with emblems specified as GEmblemedIcon

* BtkFileChooser has a GFile-oriented API now, functions
  for creating filechoosers with specific backends have been
  deprecated, since BUNNYIO is used directly.
 
* BtkAdjustment has been sealed, adding getters and setters
  for all struct fields.

* Bugs fixed:
 544265 BDK assumes XFIXES extension
 543915 "Sole completion" translation issue
 544510 SetTimer callback signatures has the wrong type
 544390 evince crashes after clicking print
 361561 StatusIcon signals not documented as definitely public API.
 368234 Incorrect tabs rendering during reorder with rounded themes
 545976 Deprecate btk_file_chooser_*_with_backend
 545978 Make filechooser GFile API public 
 544863 btkquartz.h not included in released 2.13.5 package
 424207 printing hangs on unreachable cups server
  56070 Can't click button after setting it sensitive
 545931 small documentation typos
 344383 use po/LINGUAS
  65818 rename btk_window_set_default() and add getter for it
 539733 No way to control treeview separator height
 523950 BtkTreeModelFilter's visible function may get an empty...
 526575 Missing return type in btk_ui_manager_get_toplevels...
 429411 add style properties to set minimum progressbar w...
 429427 Add "arrow-spacing" style property to BtkRange
 544302 BtkStatusIcon should support GIcon
 339699 implement btk_print_operation_set_show_dialog for...
 538686 btkprintoperation-win32.c: devmode_from_settings
 540379 btk_tree_view_enable_model_drag_dest and ...
 544684 Win64 issue, window handles are assumed to be 32-bit
 540834 Insensitive widgets cannot be grabbed
 515596 BtkUIManager's embedded UI definition example is invalid
 534979 BtkImageMenuItem is a bin but has two children
 382291 Automatically dim the combobox when the model is empty
 545982 missing braces cause bogus warnings when using BtkBuilder
 544858 Seal BtkAdjustment

* Updated translations:
 Spanish (es)
 Galician (gl)
 Japanese (ja)
 Korean (ko)
 Norwegian bokmål (nb)
 Portugese (pt)
 Brasilian Portugese (pt_BR)
 Albanian (sq)
 Swedish (sv)


Overview of Changes from BTK+ 2.13.4 to 2.13.5
==============================================

* bdk-pixbuf:
 - Use BUNNYIO for mime type sniffing when possible

* Printing:
 - Handle paused printers and printers that don't accept jobs

* BtkBuilder:
 - Support building parts of the XML tree with the new functions
   btk_builder_add_objects_from_file, btk_builder_add_objects_from_string

