Overview of Changes from BTK+ 2.13.2 to 2.13.3
==============================================

 * Support runtime font configuration changes
 
 * Use BUNNYIO for mime information

 * Use BUNNYIO directly for the file chooser, do not load filesystem
   implementation modules. This change causes some regressions on Win32, 
   which will be addressed by improved Win32 support in BUNNYIO.

 * BTK+ no longer uses translations when the application is not
   translated to the current locale
 
 * Bugs fixed: 
 520874 Should use bunnyio directly
 536185 monitor font configuration
 536757 openoffice.org menus are placed at wrong position
 536990 updateiconcache.c: 'close ()' is redundant 
 535608 do not string-copy accel paths in the menu code
 488119 critical warnings from btk_tree_view_get_visible_range
 536730 memory corruption in btktreeview
 131920 btkNotebook sends incorrect switch_page value
 526987 BtkCellRendererCombo should allow model to be NULL
 536765 BtkComboBox should set COMBO type hint for its menu
 503071 Application direction changes to right to left even if...
 517706 Connecting BtkButton with "use-stock" == FALSE to a...
 519092 Add accessibility support to BtkVolumeButton
 524222 BtkToolbar with mix of buttons with and without icons...
 537985 btk_init_with_args() doesn't open a display after...
 531960 crash in eog-image.c:1154: (priv->image != NULL)
 408154 Change BtkEntryCompletion max-items to style property...
 506853 btk_tree_view_enable_model_drag_[source|dest] problem
 536430 Libs and Cflags paths in bail-uninstalled.pc.in are out o...
 537685 print to file crashes when the target can not be written 

* Updated translations:
 Arabic (ar)
 Czech (cs)
 Estonian (et)
 Hebrew (he)
 Norwegian bokmål (nb)
 Thai (th)


Overview of Changes from BTK+ 2.13.1 to 2.13.2
==============================================

 * Fix an oversight in the header cleanup that went into 2.13.1, which
   removed btkmarshal.h from the set of headers pulled in by btk.h
 
 * Add a function to retrieve the XID of a status icon, to allow
   notification bubbles to follow the icon
 
 * Bugs fixed:
 533108 leak of GDI rebunnyion in function 'handle_wm_paint'
 530146 Setting non-string tooltip with btk_tree_view_set_tooltip_column...
 535830 wrong content type adding an item
 536126 btk.h don't include btkmarshal.h
 535497 Print preview doesn't work
 535862 btk_action_create_icon can't create icons from the icon themes
 536092 BtkEntryCompletion's popup window should set type hint
 535303 add _get_implementation to BtkStatusIcon

 * Updated translations:
 Estonian (et)
 Galician (gl)
 Italian (it)
 Vietnamese (vi)


Overview of Changes from BTK+ 2.13.0 to 2.13.1
==============================================

 * Add BtkMountOperation, a subclass of GMountOperation that
   can show password dialogs when mounting volumes

 * Add GDI+-based pixbuf loaders for bmp, emf, gif, ico, jpeg, tiff, wmf

 * Add support for pixmap redirection, new api includes the 
   btk_widget_get_snapshot() function and the BtkWidget::damage-event 
   signal and the lower-level bdk_window_redirect_to_drawable() and
   bdk_window_remove_redirection() functions

 * Add btk_show_uri(), a replacement for bunny_vfs_url_show() and
   bunny_url_show()

 * Add a "changed" signal to BtkCellRendererCombo
 
 * Sync keysyms and compose sequences with recent X.org 

 * BtkBuilder
   - supports custom stock icons 
   - supports Bango attributes in labels
 
 * BtkRecentManager
   - uses BUNNYIO to monitor .recently-used.xbel
   - limits the growth of .recently-used.xbel with a 
     btk-recent-files-max-age setting

 * Filechooser autocompletion has been reworked

 * The cups print backend displays printer status information
 
 * On OS X, accelerators are displayed using Unicode characters,
   matching the native behaviour

 * BtkIconTheme and BtkImage support GIcon

 * Bugs fixed: too many to list here
 
 * New and updated translations:
 Arabic (ar)
 Valencian-Catalan (ca)
 German (de)
 Canadian English (en_CA)
 British English (en_GB)
 Spanish (es)
 Estonian (et)
 Galician (gl)
 Hebrew (he)
 Hungarian (hu)
 Kannada (kn)
 Norwegian bokmål (nb)
 Dutch (nl)
 Norwegian Nynorsk (nn)
 Occitan (oc)
 Slovak (sk)
 Albanian (sq)
 Swedish (sv)
 Telugu (te)
 Vietnamese (vi)


Overview of Changes from BTK+ 2.12.x to 2.13.0
==============================================

 * bdk-pixbuf:
  - Support loading the OS X icns format
  - Support loading of JPEG2000 images
  - Support loading from and saving to BUNNYIO streams

 * BDK:
  - Add BdkAppLaunchContext, to provide startup notification
    with g_app_info_launch()
  - Use RandR 1.2 instead of Xinerama when available, and expose
    more monitor information

 * Accessibility:
  - The bail module is now shipped as part of BTK+
  - BtkStatusIcon supports keyboard navigation 

 * BtkCalendar:
  - Support displaying details for each day

 * BtkBuilder:
  - btk-builder-convert has been improved
  - Translation-domain works properly
  - Support accessibility

 * Testing support:
  - Add utilities for testing BTK+ applications
  - Add some unit tests for BTK+ 

 * New settings:
  - for disabling display of accelerators and mnemonics
  - for position of vertical scrollbars in scrolled windows
  - for the default input method 

 * BtkToolShell: new interface for containers of BtkToolItems

 * Bug fixes:
 - too many to list here

 * Updated translations:
  Arabic (ar)
  Assamese (as)
  Belarusian (be)
  Belarusian Latin (be@latin)
  Czech (cs)
  German (de)
  Greek (el)
  Estonian (et)
  Finnish (fi)
  French (fr)
  Irish (ga)
  Hebrew (he)
  Indonesian (id)
  Kurdish (ku)
  Marathi (mr)
  Norwegian bokmål (nb)
  Occitan (oc)
  Brazilian Portugese (pt_BR)
  Slovenian (sl)
  Swedish (sv)
  Telugu (te)
  Russian (ru)


