Overview of Changes from BTK+ 2.11.5 to 2.11.6
==============================================

 * BtkBuilder:
 - The btk-builder-convert script is more versatile
 - BtkBuilder suppports BdkPixbuf properties
 - BtkBuilder parses, but doesn't yet implement <accessibility> 
 - Support for accelerators in actions has been added

* BtkTooltips:
 - The old tooltips API has been deprecated
 - The has-tooltip property has getter and setter

* BtkTreeView: 
 - Convenience API to set tooltips: btk_tree_view_set_tooltip_row(),
   btk_tree_view_set_tooltip_cell(), btk_tree_view_get_tooltip_context(),
   btk_tree_view_set_tooltip_column()

* BtkIconView:
 - Convenience API to set tooltips: btk_icon_view_set_tooltip_item(),
   btk_icon_view_set_tooltip_cell(), btk_icon_view_get_tooltip_context(),
   btk_icon_view_set_tooltip_column()

* Bug fixes:
