 Korean (ko)
 Norwegian bokmål (nb)
 Russian (ru)
 Sinhala (si)
 Vietnamese (vi)


Overview of Changes from BTK+ 2.11.3 to 2.11.4
==============================================

* The multipress input method correctly handles control keys

* The memory management of BtkRecentManager has been
  changed, deprecating the screen-related functions in favour
  of btk_recent_manager_get_default().

* Bugs fixed: 
 448928 Some BtkBuildable methods named too generically
 448193 btkbuilder.h causes compile error with C++
 354887 BtkFileChooserButton displays unnecessary authentication ...
