Overview of Changes from BTK+ 2.11.2 to 2.11.3
==============================================

* BtkBuilder: BTK+ supports constructing user interfaces 
  from XML descriptions now, similar to libglade.

* The new tooltip code now has convenience api to set
  text tooltips: btk_widget_set_tooltip_text(),
  btk_widget_set_tooltip_markup()
 
* BtkTextView, BtkEntry:
 - btk_widget_modify_cursor() is a new function in the 
   btk_widget_modify family to override the style-provided 
   cursor colors
 - Use a block cursor in overwrite mode

* BtkFileChooser:
 - Use xdg-user-dirs to find the Desktop directory
 - btk_file_system_create() is now public API

* BtkMenu:
 - BtkMenuItem gained a submenu property
 - BtkMenuShell obtained a move-selected signal 

* OS X port:
 - Many improvements

* Bugs fixed:
 445691 Crash when spawning a new process
 447163 Implicit pointer conversion bdk_font_ref()
 420249 deadlock on print operation
 440918 out-of-bound access on loading pnm
 142494 treeview coordinate systems need documentation/auditing
 343012 RC parser rejects lower-case identifiers.
 350460 Popup windows (esp. menus) misbehave wrt focus
 410815 Icon view gets confused when scaling down the pixbuf column
 435471 small BtkComboBox cleanup
 435840 BTK_WIDGET_SAVED_STATE inconsistency
 442617 bdk_spawn overrides envp, breaking child setup funcs whic...
 443913 When .recently-used.xbel is empty, recently-used uses %10...
 444097 Cannot compile btksearchenginesimple.c
 444310 update_buttons_state on a bare assistant causes btk+ to c...
 444734 Compact file-chooser folder selection not working with gt...
 444786 Error loading 'btk-select-color' in Stock icons and Items
 445054 BtkScrolledWindow::scrollbars-within-bevel is drawing wrong
 445284 Custom (pixbuf etc.) cursor reverts to default cursor on ...
 445539 Unititialized var in btkrc.c trunk
 445855 btk_scale_button_new() uses private API.
 446138 Tiny doc update for bdk_window_get_pointer()
 446513 btknotebook.h: create_window is wrong declaration
 446616 bunnylib requirement insufficient
 447065 BtkMenuItem: add "submenu" property and some cleanup
