* New and updated translations (bg,bn_IN,de,dz,el,es,
  et,eu,fi,gu,hu,ko,ku,ja,lt,mk,ml,nb,ne,nl,or,pl,po,
  sv,th,tr,tt,uk,zh_HK,zh_TW)


