Overview of Changes from BTK+ 2.9.3 to 2.9.4
============================================

* BtkPrintOperation:
 - UI improvements in the print dialog
 - Make printing work without a display connection
 - Replace "Print to PDF" by "Print to file" that
   can generate PDF or PostScript
 - Add a function to the low-level API to 
   enumerate all printers

* BtkNotebook tab DND has been improved

* BtkProgressbar supports text in activity mode 

* BtkLabel allows to set the wrap mode

* BtkStatusIcon supports transparency

* Bugs fixed:
 344850 Dragging a BtkTreeViewColumn segfaults when 
        using certain BtkTreeViewColumnDropFunc
