Overview of Changes from BTK+ 2.9.2 to 2.9.3
============================================  

* BtkPrintOperation: 
 - Introduce an allow-async property 
 - Introduce a BtkPrintOperationAction enumeration
 - Rename pdf_target to export_filename
 - Allow to hide "Print to PDF" in the low-level API

* BtkNotebook:
 - Add a destroy notify to 
   btk_notebook_set_window_creation_hook.

* BtkTreeView:
 - Support grid lines

* BtkRange:
 - Add a number of new stle properties which allow more
   fexible stepper theming

* Bugs fixed:
 153212 Have the Paste kbd shortcut jump to the location in 
        the buffer
 337491 _bdk_win32_drawable_release_dc: DeleteDC() called on 
        a GetDC() handle
 339739 btk/btkprintoperation-win32.c: 3 compile error
 342339 BtkRange::stepper-spacing style property not 
        implemented correctly
 343945 Buttons of a BtkAssistant are not accessible
 344148 Wrong reqs for BATK
 344209 btk_notebook_set_window_creation_hook() has no destroy 
        func.
 344232 BtkEntry's "Delete" context menu item is sensitive on a 
        non-editable BtkEntry
 344244 Window resizing not working when keeping the aspect 
        fixed
 344288 btk_print_operation_preview_is_selected must return 
        a value
 344386 bdk-2.0-uninstalled.pc.in and bdkconfig.h
 344496 CRLF converting via Clipboard
 344504 BtkPrintCapabilities not in btktypebuiltins.h
 344505 Wrong signal registration for create_custom_widget
 344512 cvs build issue
