  - Various memleak, ref counting fixes [Jonathan, Jorn Baayen, Daniel 
    Elstner, Morten Welinder]
  - btk_tree_selection_selected_foreach now immediately returns if 
    the model is being changed [Havoc Pennington]
  - Fix evil bug with insertions to BtkTreeModelSort [Hans Petter Jansson]
